snippet.title: AMBER GUYGER APPEALS | BOTHAM JEANS MUM REACTION | JOSHUA BROWN DEATH | MY THOUGHTS
snippet.description:
Hi my lovely turtles, 
Please don't forget to LIKE, SHARE, COMMENT, SUBSCRIBE & HIT THE BELL to be the first to know whats up!
I just wanted to share my thoughts on this AMBER GUYGER APPEAL and once again present my sincere and deepest condolences to BOTHAM JEANS FAMILY! Particularly his mom, I can't even fathom how she feels...

I first heard about the store on Lovelity2002 channel you can watch it here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oCwyfGe6lQ8

Shout out to 4itrox here is a link to her channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/4itsrox

BOTHAM JEANS ARTICLE HERE https://www.nbcnews.com/news/crime-courts/amber-guyger-sentencing-resumes-after-murder-conviction-death-botham-jean-n1061146

JOSHUA BROWN ARTICLE https://edition.cnn.com/2019/12/09/us/amber-guyger-witness-murder/index.html

BOTHAM JEANS MOM REACTION FROM ST LUCIA HERE
https://www.kdrv.com/content/news/562157662.html

Let me know your thoughts in the comments below...
